#Update The footprints of Governor Udom Emmanuel in the “Raffia Zone” – Ikot Ekpene Senatorial District of the state will remain indelible for generations to come, with such projects like the Model Girls Secondary School, Ikot Ekang in Abak LGA. The Model Girls Secondary School, in Ikot Ekang is one of Governor Udom Emmanuel’s pilot model schools in the state established as part of the Governor’s commitment towards ensuring that every Akwa Ibom child has quality basic education. The Governor has ensured the provision of basic infrastructure for the school to provide it with a conducive learning environment. Furthermore, an access road has been constructed into the Model Girls Secondary school, which is adjudged one of the best in the country in terms of personnel, students performance and Curriculum. See the reason Governor Udom Emmanuel is held in high esteem by the people of Ikot Ekpene senatorial district? Yes… That’s Udom in the Raffia zone. More to come.       #udominraffiazone!!!
